JSLint Reporter
Node.js wrapper for JSLint (http://jslint.com)


Usage:

  $ node wrapper.js [options] <filepath>

(use `node wrapper.js --upgrade` to generate jslint.js alongside wrapper.js)


Options:

  --<name>[=<value>]
    names as per http://www.jslint.com/lint.html#options
    (e.g. "--strict --predef=foo,bar,baz --maxlen=80")

  --goodparts
    shortcut for recommended options
    NB: Individual recommendations can be overridden by specifying the
        respective option separately (e.g. "--goodparts --onevar=false").

  --upgrade
    download latest version of JSLint

  --version
    display JSLint Reporter version number
